Name: MSX_a05 [Pub]
Description:
EnemiesNoSync Edition, For Pubbing. REQUIRES CD2 B15+. Elite Restriction Release made its HARDER ND-flavored difficulty but use mostly Vanilla Assets, expect to see many new Elites spawn along the way. Partially inspired by zeta's Death Series.
    Alpha 05:
  - [MEV] Removed Elite Korlok Sprout due to visibility problem, Elite Spitballer is now back in the fray.
  - Elite Spitballer projectile changed from Lacerator's Stomp to charged EPC projectile (Damage dealt is higher than a korlok's shot, but projectile can be shot down). Additionally DifficultyRating 175 -> 150.
  - Rockpox Breeder: Reduce breeding interval.
  - Enemy Diversity: Swapped chance to get 1-3 and 7-10 bins, so now it's less likely to get super diversity wave, and more chance for low diversity waves.
  - NormalWaveDifficulty: Lowered chance to get Fat Wave from 20% to 10%.
  - Grunt: MaxSpawnCount reduced 160 -> 120.
  - Swarmer: MaxSpawnCount reduced 200 -> 120.
  - Acid Spitter and Web Spitter: Capped MaxSpawnCount to 70.
  - Rarity increase: Crawler (3.5 -> 5), Youngling/Shocker (5.125 -> 5.25), Stingtail/Shellback/Fire Bomber (5.25 -> 5.375), Stalker/Grabber/Trawler/Patrol Bot (5.25 -> 5.5)
  - DifficultyRating increase: Menace (47.5 -> 55), Acid Spitter (35 -> 40), Shellback (70 -> 85),  Goo Bomber (47.5 -> 50), Warden/Trawler (45 -> 50), Youngling (30 -> 35), Praetorian (10 -> 30), Rockpox Exploder (10 -> 15).
  - Sniper Turret and its variants now has increased DifficultyRating.
  - Barrage Infector now has a MaxSpawnCount cap of 3 (lowered to 2 in Escort).
  - Elite Barrager DifficultyRating +50 (300 -> 350/550 -> 600).
  - Elite Burst Turret DifficultyRating -25 (200 -> 175).
  - Vartok now has increased DifficultyRating to 200.
  - Nexus, normal Turret enemies SpawnAmountModifier is now 0.5.
  - Oppressor now has a cap of 3 -> 2 normally.
